import styled from 'styled-components'


export const InputContainer = styled.div ({

    width: '100%',
    height: '80px',
    backgroundColor: 'green',

    display: 'flex',
    alignItems: 'center',
    justifyContent: 'flex-end',

    fontSize: '24px',
    fontFamily: 'Roboto',

    Input:{
        width: '100%',
        height: '80px',
        backgroundColor: '#ce4bba',
        border: '0px',
        alignItems: 'right',
        padding: '0 10px',
        fontSize: '24px',
        fontFamily: 'Roboto',
        color: 'white',



    },
})
